{
  "chapter": 189,
  "chapter_summary": "项少龙路经琴府探望琴清，两人因误会发生争执，琴清以为项少龙用美男计讨好朱姬才获支持，后琴清主动到乌府澄清，二人和好。与此同时，项少龙与纪嫣然商议对付吕不韦借《吕氏春秋》造势之策，纪嫣然提出以恩师邹衍的《五德终始说》反击，主张秦得水德、克周火德，将储君塑造成应运而生的圣人。项少龙更灵机一触，提议炮制黑龙符瑞以造势。众人入宫觐见小盘，纪嫣然详述五德之理，琴清引孟子之言佐证，李斯、王陵、昌平君等各有建言，最终小盘下令秘密推行此计划，配合新官制改革以压制吕不韦。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_qin_qing",
      "text": "我只是匆匆路过，让我向琴太傅打个招呼便成。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 189,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_qing",
      "speaker_name": "琴清",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "噢！是你！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 189,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_qin_qing",
      "text": "琴太傅你好！请恕项少龙迟来问候之罪。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 189,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_qin_qing",
      "text": "琴太傅绣的是什么图案纹饰？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 189,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_qing",
      "speaker_name": "琴清",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项大人检点些好吗？怎可与琴清共坐一席呢？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 189,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_qin_qing",
      "text": "我只是来打个招呼，立即要走，就算无礼也仅片刻之事，琴太傅可否纵容在下一会儿？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 189,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_qing",
      "speaker_name": "琴清",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你这人哩！偏要这么闯进来，人家又是衣鬓不整的。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 189,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_qin_qing",
      "text": "我却一点不如是想，若非如此，便欣赏不到琴太傅娇慵动人的姿采。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 189,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_qin_qing",
      "text": "见到我安然回来，心中欢喜吗？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 189,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_qing",
      "speaker_name": "琴清",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项大人不是还有很多事赶着去办吗？莫要把光阴浪费在这里。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 189,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_qing",
      "speaker_name": "琴清",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项少龙！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 189,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_qin_qing",
      "text": "琴太傅有何指教？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 189,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_qing",
      "speaker_name": "琴清",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你恼了吗？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 189,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_qin_qing",
      "text": "若你是我，会高兴吗？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 189,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_qing",
      "speaker_name": "琴清",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "当然不高兴哪！可是你知否刚才的行为，实在太不尊重人家呢！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 189,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_qin_qing",
      "text": "是我不对！琴太傅请见谅。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 189,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_qing",
      "speaker_name": "琴清",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项少龙，答琴清一个问题好吗？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 189,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_qin_qing",
      "text": "琴太傅请下问。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 189,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_qing",
      "speaker_name": "琴清",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你究竟使了什么手段，使太后同意让昌平君当上左丞相呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 189,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_qin_qing",
      "text": "琴太傅原来对我项少龙这般没有信心，罢了！你爱怎猜就怎么猜，横竖我也给你误会惯了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 189,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_ying",
      "speaker_name": "嬴盈",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项大人你好！为何回来这么多天，仍不来探望人家呢？",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 189,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ying_ying",
      "text": "嬴大小姐会有空吗？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 189,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "夫君大人是否受到挫折，否则怎会一脸忿然之色？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 189,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "噢！不要亲人家那里好吗？教人怎为你筹谋呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 189,
      "line_start": 123,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "早知你定有办法的。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 189,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我也看过《吕氏春秋》，确是本不朽巨著，但最弱的一环，却是吕不韦拾人牙慧的理论；比起我干爹，他是差远了。最致命处是不合时宜，只要我把干爹的《五德终始说》搬出来，包保可盖过他的高调空言。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 189,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 133
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "干爹的《五德终始说》不是一种预言学吗？怎派得上用场？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 189,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "纪才女这就陪我入宫见驾如何？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 189,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 149
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "人家现在这么舒服，明天入宫好吗？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 189,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "不！出嫁从夫，纪才女要立即陪我去才行。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 189,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你去招呼清姊，人家换好衣服，再陪你入宫吧！谁叫我纪嫣然嫁了给你哩！",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 189,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 161
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_qin_qing",
      "text": "对不起！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 189,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_qing",
      "speaker_name": "琴清",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项少龙！琴清今趟来拜访，是要和你弄清楚一件事。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 189,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_qin_qing",
      "text": "若只是违心之言，就不要说好了，我已不再骗自己，但望琴太傅也向我这好榜样多多学习，哈！",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 189,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_qing",
      "speaker_name": "琴清",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "琴清何时说过违心之言？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 189,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_qin_qing",
      "text": "那就最好，现在我要和嫣然入宫觐见储君，琴太傅和我们一道去吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 189,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_qing",
      "speaker_name": "琴清",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "什么事要劳动我们的纪才女呢？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 189,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiao_pan",
      "text": "五德转移，治各有宜，而符应若兹。所以能一统天下者，必须得到五行中其中一德才成。五德就是金、水、木、火、土，每德到了一定时期就会衰落，而另一德代之而兴。黄帝得的是土德；接着是木克土，故夏禹得木德；金克木，商汤得金德；火克金，周文王得火德；现今周朝衰败，乘时而起的，该是克火的水德。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 189,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "水克火！水克火！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 189,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "王陵",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "老臣知道邹衍大家学究天人，但终是一家之言，未知是否有任何根据呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 189,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_wang_ling",
      "text": "五行之说，早见于《尚书》之内，所谓'水曰润下、火曰炎上、木曰曲直，金曰从革，土爰稼穑'是也。自古以来，便有'天有六气，降生五味，发为五色，征为五声'之说，五味就是金味辛，木味酸，水味咸，火味苦，土味甘。故声有五，是为宫、商、角、征、羽；味有酸、苦、甘、辛、咸；色则为青、赤、黄、白、黑，均与五行相配合，相生相克，循环不休。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 189,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_qing",
      "speaker_name": "琴清",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "孟子也有言：'五百年必有王者兴。''由尧舜至于汤，五百有余岁；由汤至于文王，五百有余岁；由文王至于孔子，五百有余岁'，正是五德交替的现象。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 189,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_si",
      "speaker_name": "李斯",
      "listener": "char_xiao_pan",
      "text": "孔子顶多只是个贤人，哪有资格称王者，我看该是轮到储君了。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 189,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "谁是孟子口中所指每五百年多便出世的王者，只是空口白话，怎样方可拿来打击吕不韦的谬言？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 189,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_pan",
      "text": "靠的当然是宣扬的手法和才女干爹邹先生的权威，试问谁比邹先生更有资格判断谁是新圣人，哪到别人不心服。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 189,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_pan",
      "text": "我们便利用'五德终始说'，同时推行李大人草议三公九卿的新官制，定可重整朝政，不让吕不韦肆无忌惮的横行下去。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 189,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiao_pan",
      "text": "这叫'以子之矛，攻子之盾'，因为《吕氏春秋》采的是各家之言，包括干爹的'五德终始说'在内，其中的〈应同〉篇便记载了'凡帝王者之将兴也，天必先见祥乎下民。黄帝之时，天先见大螾大蝼。黄帝曰：'士气胜。'士气胜，故其色尚黄，其事则土'等语。又说'代火者必将水，天且先见水气胜，水气胜，故其色尚黑，其事则水'，所以只要我们藉吕不韦弘扬《吕氏春秋》之势，只采其'五德终始说'，明褒实贬，吕不韦只好有苦自己知了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 189,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "如此就好办了。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 189,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "王陵",
      "listener": "char_xiao_pan",
      "text": "刚才纪才女不是说过五德转移，新圣人出世时，必有符瑞之应。如黄帝见大蝼，文王见火赤鸟衔丹书集于周社，若储君不得符瑞，恐怕仍不能令天下人心服哩！",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 189,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_pan",
      "text": "这事容易至极，只要储君往祭某河之时，我们使人炮制一条能在河面翻腾的黑龙，像尼斯湖水怪……嘿！没有什么，只要略露背鳍，我们即可指其为符瑞，那一切不合理的事，都有了支持。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 189,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_ping_jun",
      "speaker_name": "昌平君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这事说来容易，但假若被人揭穿，岂非是天大笑话。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 189,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_chang_ping_jun",
      "text": "这事包在我身上，黑龙只要有几下动作，迅即隐去，我们便大功告成，保证没人可以看破。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 189,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
