      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这事拜托太傅了。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 189,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "寡人若得水德，定须有仪式和各方面的配合才成，请才女为寡人拟定计划，以便到时执行。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 189,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此事只限今天与会之人知悉，若寡人发觉任何人漏出消息，必会追究，绝不饶恕。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 189,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 278
    }
